  "pageTitle": "請告訴我們您的廢棄物回收專案",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"contact-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">聯絡方式 / 詢問</p>\n        <h1 id=\"contact-title\">請告訴我們您的廢棄物回收專案</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">若想獲得更實用的建議，請分享您的廢棄物類型、目標容量、場址限制、目的地國家及考慮的產品方向。這給WEI LAN足夠的背景，讓工程討論能正式開始。</p>\n        <div class=\"page-chip-row\" aria-label=\"專案資訊重點\">\n          <span>廢棄物類型</span>\n          <span>容量目標</span>\n          <span>場地區域</span>\n          <span>輸出目標</span>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"contact-section\" aria-labelledby=\"form-title\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">專案諮詢</p>\n          <h2 id=\"form-title\">請寄送你的資料、目標容量和場地限制</h2>\n          <p>收到您的專案 詳情 後，工程團隊可檢視廢棄物流、容量目標、現場狀況及自動化預期，並建議合適的系統配置路徑。</p>\n          <div class=\"process-list\" aria-label=\"後續流程\">\n            <span>工程審查</span>\n            <span>配置建議</span>\n            <span>技術提案</span>\n            <span>報價討論</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <form class=\"contact-form\" data-contact-form action=\"/api/contact\" method=\"post\">\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            名稱\n            <input name=\"name\" autocomplete=\"name\" required>\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            電子郵件\n            <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" autocomplete=\"email\" required>\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            公司\n            <input name=\"company\" autocomplete=\"organization\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            WhatsApp / 電話\n            <input name=\"phone\" autocomplete=\"tel\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-narrow\">\n            國家/地區\n            <input name=\"country\" autocomplete=\"country-name\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-narrow\">\n            目標容量\n            <input name=\"capacity\" placeholder=\"範例：2 t/h或100 t/h\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-narrow\">\n            可用 網站區域\n            <input name=\"siteArea\" placeholder=\"廠區面積或佈局限制\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-full\">\n            產品興趣\n            <span class=\"product-interest-picker\" data-product-picker>\n              <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"product\" data-product-value required>\n              <button class=\"product-interest-control\" type=\"button\" data-product-control aria-haspopup=\"listbox\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                <span data-product-label>選擇產品線</span>\n                <span class=\"product-interest-chevron\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              </button>\n              <span class=\"product-interest-menu\" data-product-menu role=\"listbox\" aria-label=\"產品興趣\">\n                <button class=\"product-interest-option\" type=\"button\" data-product-option=\"AI optical sorting center\" role=\"option\">AI光學分揀中心</button>\n                <button class=\"product-interest-option\" type=\"button\" data-product-option=\"Construction and bulky waste recycling line\" role=\"option\">建築與大型廢棄物回收線</button>\n                <button class=\"product-interest-option\" type=\"button\" data-product-option=\"Both systems\" role=\"option\">兩種系統</button>\n              </span>\n            </span>\n          </label>\n          <div class=\"form-field form-field-full waste-type-field\" data-waste-type-field>\n            <span class=\"field-label\" id=\"waste-type-label\">廢棄物類型</span>\n            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wasteType\" data-waste-type-value>\n            <div class=\"waste-type-picker\" data-waste-picker>\n              <button class=\"waste-type-control is-placeholder\" type=\"button\" data-waste-control aria-labelledby=\"waste-type-label\" aria-haspopup=\"listbox\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-disabled=\"true\" disabled>\n                <span data-waste-label>先選擇產品線</span>\n                <span class=\"waste-type-chevron\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              </button>\n              <div class=\"waste-type-menu\" data-waste-menu>\n                <div class=\"waste-type-options\" data-waste-options role=\"listbox\" aria-label=\"廢棄物類型建議\"></div>\n                <div class=\"waste-type-create-row\">\n                  <input data-waste-custom autocomplete=\"off\" placeholder=\"類型 自訂廢棄物類型\">\n                  <button class=\"waste-type-custom-clear\" type=\"button\" data-waste-custom-clear aria-label=\"清除自訂廢棄物類型\">×</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"waste-type-menu-actions\">\n                  <button class=\"waste-type-clear\" type=\"button\" data-waste-clear>全部</button>\n                  <button class=\"waste-type-done\" type=\"button\" data-waste-done>完成</button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-full\">\n            詳情計畫\n            <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" placeholder=\"材料組成、輸出目標、電壓、自動化需求、時間表\" required></textarea>\n          </label>\n          <div class=\"form-submit-row\">\n            <p class=\"contact-note\">銷售熱線：+86 137 8001 2268 / +86 180 6737 7770</p>\n            <button type=\"submit\">請求工程提案</button>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"form-status\" data-contact-status role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\"></p>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section service-section\" aria-labelledby=\"next-steps-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">後續流程</p>\n          <h2 id=\"next-steps-title\">從詢問到提案討論的簡單路徑</h2>\n          <p>大多數專案一開始不需要長時間的探索階段。一個明確的初步徵求意見書通常就足以進入實務技術審查。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-grid\">\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">01</span>\n            <h3>提交專案 詳情</h3>\n            <p>傳送廢棄物類型、目標容量及廠廠限制，讓團隊了解營運情境。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">02</span>\n            <h3>工程審查</h3>\n            <p>WEI LAN在討論配置前，會先檢視物料類型、可能的製程模組以及整體專案方向。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">03</span>\n            <h3>系統建議</h3>\n            <p>團隊建議最適合的產品線、流程路徑及配置範圍，以進行更深入的評估。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">04</span>\n            <h3>提案與報價討論</h3>\n            <p>一旦基本契合度明確，對話便可進入文件、參數及商業討論。</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section dark-section\" aria-labelledby=\"checklist-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">查詢清單</p>\n          <h2 id=\"checklist-title\">提升提案品質最快的四個輸入</h2>\n          <p>即使是簡短的第一則訊息，只要包含以下操作基本事項，也會更具可行性。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-grid\">\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">輸入01</span>\n            <h3>廢棄物類型與組成</h3>\n            <p>釐清材料是PET、HDPE、PP、混合塑膠、C&D 廢棄物、裝飾廢棄物還是大塊廢棄物。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">輸入02</span>\n            <h3>目標容量</h3>\n            <p>分享預期的每小時吞吐量，讓建議能維持在合適的型號與模組範圍內。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">輸入03</span>\n            <h3>場地條件</h3>\n            <p>可用可調整的佔地面積、佈局限制、電壓及局部操作限制都會影響解的方向。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">輸入04</span>\n            <h3>預期產出</h3>\n            <p>例如ai在你希望系統達到的回收產品、純度目標或最終材料方向，這樣可以選擇支援。</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"cta-band\" aria-labelledby=\"rfq-support-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">需要更多背景嗎？</p>\n        <h2 id=\"rfq-support-title\">您也可以在寄出表格前先檢視產品、解決方案和資源</h2>\n        <p>如果團隊仍在比較選項，請使用 配套 頁面縮小專案方向，然後返回最相關的廢棄物流與容量目標。</p>\n        <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/products\">探索產品線</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">評論資源</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
